{"id":"bd159983-96bd-474e-b82e-bbfed6aef4c0","name":"Jeong Ujin || The beginning ","description":"<p><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">You’re a newcomer in the entertainment industry, just starting out with small extra roles. One day, on set, you cross paths with Jeong Ujin—a famous and wealthy star with a reputation that precedes him. Rumor has it he’s helped many rising actors reach the spotlight, but always in exchange for sleeping with him. Now, he’s showing interest in you. If it were you, would you accept his offer or reject it?</span></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Vyon9YQ5wpOfETcI79MaN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 0, 216);\"><strong><u>Jeong brothers</u></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4fda7dfb-867b-4b74-80f2-c36128901de3_character-jeong-ji-hoon-unforgettable-night\" target=\"_blank\">First brother - Ji Hoon</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7e86ba17-8114-4d20-9770-2105d150f43a_character-jeong-ji-hoon-alt\" target=\"_blank\">Ji Hoon’s ALT 20K celebration</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2604f1fa-4218-4501-9474-df60eaee3f3f_character-jeong-chris-the-blind-date\" target=\"_blank\">Second brother - Chris</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/449f7f30-8d76-471e-b610-e370a83b5016_character-jeong-chris-alt\" target=\"_blank\">Chris’s ALT 20K celebration</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/62050e7b-8e3c-44fc-82bb-8ed63c46f989_character-jeong-ujin-the-actor\" target=\"_blank\">Third brother - Ujin</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3bfa87dc-3f68-4ace-b6ac-6f39bdd13f84_character-jeong-ujin-alt\" target=\"_blank\">Ujin’s ALT 20K celebration</a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/38fd380b-faef-45b3-9418-c6c390f52350_character-jeong-ji-hoon-alt\" target=\"_blank\">Emi’s Birthday Special Alt Ji Hoon</a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/46c851a4-cb44-49c0-a8d1-ffa1c2fac2f4_character-jeong-ji-hoon-the-beginning-alt\" target=\"_blank\">Ji Hoon’s beginning Alt requested by Darla</a></p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/PE4tdLRFlpr5T0QMrg6Ip.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p>Thank you so much, Paper, for supporting me with Ujin’s ALT. I’m really sorry it came later than I promised—this month has been so busy. I truly hope you enjoy your time with Ujin!</p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">I kinda disappeared for three days, didn’t I? 😂 With so many upcoming events lined up in October, November, and December, I’ve been really caught up with work. Finally got a chance to breathe again—so I’m back, lol!</span></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/vZa4gVyY\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tNOzl9yTJaCyAEJ4ZAaPw.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/vZa4gVyY\" target=\"_blank\">DISCORD SERVER</a></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">join the 18+ (id checked) discord <em>server with </em><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/e28f6d6c-6cbf-4aba-a9f5-b6bd2e0a7634_profile-of-%E2%84%8B%E2%84%B4-%F0%9D%93%85-%E2%84%AF-%F0%9D%95%B9-%F0%9D%92%A6-%F0%9D%92%B6-%F0%9D%92%B9-%E2%84%AF-%F0%9D%93%83\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Kaden &amp; </em></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6d5e9470-1398-47b8-817f-5d29034